      <h1 class='title'>Healthy Living Centres</h1>
    </div>
    <div class='commons-written-statements-sitting' id='content'>
      
      <cite class='section'>HC Deb 16 September 2004 vol 424 c1759WS</cite>
      <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_1759ws' title='Col. 1759WS &mdash; HC Deb 16 September 2004 vol 424 c1759WS' name='column_1759ws' href='#column_1759ws' rel='bookmark'>1759WS</a>
      <div class='hentry member_contribution'>
        <a name='S6CV0424P2_20040916_CWS2_596'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-don-foster' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0424P2_20040916_CWS2_596' title='Link to this speech by Mr Don Foster' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-don-foster" title="Mr Don Foster">Mr. Don Foster</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para">To ask the Secretary of State for Health how much Exchequer funding has been received by healthy living centres since 1999, broken down by region; and if he will make a statement. [188744]</p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution'>
        <a name='S6CV0424P2_20040916_CWS2_597'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/miss-melanie-johnson' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0424P2_20040916_CWS2_597' title='Link to this speech by Miss Melanie Johnson' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/miss-melanie-johnson" title="Miss Melanie Johnson">Miss Melanie Johnson</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para">Healthy living centres (HLCs) are funded by the Big Lottery Fund programme and do not receive funding from the Department. Many HLC plans included funds from statutory bodies, including the national health service and local authorities. The amounts actually provided and the regional distribution are not held centrally.</p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution'>
        <a name='S6CV0424P2_20040916_CWS2_598'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-don-foster' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0424P2_20040916_CWS2_598' title='Link to this speech by Mr Don Foster' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-don-foster" title="Mr Don Foster">Mr. Don Foster</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para">To ask the Secretary of State for Health how many healthy living centres have<span class="italic">(a)</span> opened, <span class="italic">(b)</span> closed and <span class="italic">(c)</span> have discussed the possibility of closure with his Department since 1999; and if he will make a statement. [188745]</p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution'>
        <a name='S6CV0424P2_20040916_CWS2_599'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/miss-melanie-johnson' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0424P2_20040916_CWS2_599' title='Link to this speech by Miss Melanie Johnson' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/miss-melanie-johnson" title="Miss Melanie Johnson">Miss Melanie Johnson</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para">257 Big Lottery Fund healthy living centres have opened in England. One has closed and two have discussed the possibility of closure with their regional director of public health.</p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
